TinyUploads is a fast and simple way to get images online.  Automatically resize and upload pictures for your blog.

== Description ==

TinyUploads is a fast and simple way to get images online.  Automatically resize and upload pictures for your blog.  Choose from 3 different thumbnail sizes, write captions, re-order images, and more.  

For more information, see [TinyUploads for WordPress][http://tinyuploads.com/].

== Installation ==

1. Upload "tinyuploads.php" to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
1. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress

